<%= header_section("Your bank account holder name was rejected.") %>
<div>
  <p>Hi there. Your bank rejected the account holder name on your Gumroad payout settings. This prevents your payouts from being delivered.</p>
  <% case @country_code %>
  <% when Compliance::Countries::JPN.alpha2 %>
    <p>For Japanese bank accounts, the account holder name must be written in Katakana and exactly match the name registered with your bank.</p>
  <% when Compliance::Countries::VNM.alpha2 %>
    <p>For Vietnamese bank accounts, the account holder name must be written in unaccented Latin characters (no diacritics) and exactly match the name registered with your bank.</p>
  <% when Compliance::Countries::IDN.alpha2 %>
    <p>For Indonesian bank accounts, the account holder name must be written in Latin characters and exactly match the name registered with your bank.</p>
  <% else %>
    <p>Please make sure the account holder name exactly matches the name registered with your bank, using the characters required by your bank.</p>
  <% end %>
  <p>Please update your name in <%= link_to "your payout settings", settings_payments_url %>. Thanks!</p>
</div>
